verbose_text: The recently concluded ISCHEMIA trial of patients with stable CAD showed that initial invasive therapy provided greater improvement in angina related health status but did not reduce the risk of ischemic cardiovascular events or death from any cause compared to initial conservative therapy [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
